title: 50 Badass Blues Guitar Solos
description:
Guitar Player Magazine, February 2014, had an article choosing 50 Badass Blues Guitar Solos. I found all of them although there are a couple of exceptions as to version.  I think I've pulled all of them and added another 50 or so that I like. Enjoy. P.S. Thanks to all who unknowingly contributed to this effort through their uploads.
All are MP3 and most are 320 Mbps. The actual magazine article was scanned as PDF and is included here. If you find a song, artist or band which you like, go buy their stuff and help to feed them, especially my hometown boys from Warrensburg, Missouri, the Nace Brothers-featured on the last two songs.
